GUBERNATORSKY a mol, itster LENINA, ikh veys vu dos iz.

00:25:07.613 --> 00:25:09.590
flegn zayn di kromen.

00:25:09.590 --> 00:25:12.226
flegt alts in di kromen shteyn.

00:25:12.226 --> 00:25:17.408
fleg ikh geyn, oy, ikh fleg kukn in di kromen, k- kukn vos iz dos un vos iz dos un dos iz UNK

00:25:17.408 --> 00:25:21.862
ken nit zayn azoy az s'iz faran azoyne zakhn geshmak un s'iz faran azoyne zakhn

00:25:21.862 --> 00:25:22.931
oyf onton

00:25:22.931 --> 00:25:26.476
un biz vanen ikh fleg dergeyn in SHKOLA fleg ikh farshpetikn in SHKOLA.

00:25:26.476 --> 00:25:30.590
dos iz geven, zey, dos iz mayn PROBLEM geven, dos gedenk ikh.

00:25:30.590 --> 00:25:33.317
farshteyt?

00:25:33.317 --> 00:25:35.408
vi hot oysgezen Minsk?

00:25:35.408 --> 00:25:40.885
Minsk iz geven modern, tsi altmodish?

00:25:40.885 --> 00:25:44.022
di, di tsentralishe gasn

00:25:44.022 --> 00:25:46.045
vos heyst modern?

00:25:46.045 --> 00:25:47.499
vos heyst modern?

00:25:47.499 --> 00:25:48.954
antviklt

00:25:48.954 --> 00:25:50.817
di gasn zenen nit geven

00:25:50.817 --> 00:25:53.681
s'iz geven sheyn, sheyne BUILDINGes, ye.

00:25:53.681 --> 00:25:57.544
s'iz geven sheyninke BUILDINGes, iz geven a, a sakh.

00:25:57.544 --> 00:25:59.090
KOLNOA.

00:25:59.090 --> 00:26:01.703
far der milkhome; s'iz geven zeyer grin.

00:26:01.703 --> 00:26:04.271
s'iz geven a, a taykh geven a

00:26:04.271 --> 00:26:05.976
a ummeglekhkeyt a

00:26:05.976 --> 00:26:08.658
vi zogt men dos oyf yidish? a farshtunkene taykh.

00:26:08.658 --> 00:26:12.954
flegt ale mol, farshteyt?

00:26:12.954 --> 00:26:17.977
s'iz geven a por gasn, s'iz geven zeyer sheyne, un azoy iz geven ale

00:26:17.977 --> 00:26:20.340
hiltserne

00:26:20.340 --> 00:26:21.250
gebaydes?

00:26:21.250 --> 00:26:23.522
UNK dernokh hot men ongehoybn boyen un nokh

00:26:23.522 --> 00:26:25.568
hot men onghoybn boyen dem

00:26:25.568 --> 00:26:28.431
dem teater opera, lebn mir.

00:26:28.431 --> 00:26:32.613
zeyer a groyser, zeyer a groys, far vos zey hobn zey azoy geboyt

00:26:32.613 --> 00:26:34.612
farshtey ikh nit.

00:26:34.612 --> 00:26:38.135
zey hobn geboyt a, zeyer a groysn teater, un zey hobn geboyt a

00:26:38.135 --> 00:26:41.863
a BUILDING fun, fun MEMSHELA UNK.

00:26:41.863 --> 00:26:43.408
farshteyt?

00:26:43.408 --> 00:26:45.340
a sakh ongehoybn boyen

00:26:45.340 --> 00:26:49.113
UNK gezen az s'heybt, heybt zikh oyf, s'heybt zikh oyf sheyn.

00:26:49.113 --> 00:26:50.340
ir farshteyt?

00:26:50.340 --> 00:26:53.976
ober di tragedye vos s'hot geton zikh in Rusland

00:26:53.976 --> 00:26:59.453
fun revolutsye biz der milkhome

00:26:59.453 --> 00:27:04.271
hobn mir keyner nit gevust, ir farshteyt? me flegt shisn mentshn, mir farkhapn mentshn

00:27:04.271 --> 00:27:05.612
un me flegt,

00:27:05.612 --> 00:27:07.885
represirn mentshn

00:27:07.885 --> 00:27:10.771
un me flegt, in di, in di

00:27:10.771 --> 00:27:12.658
in SHKOLA flegt men,

00:27:12.658 --> 00:27:17.068
di PICTURES fun di, fun di MARSHAL, fun alerleyike flegt men far-

00:27:17.068 --> 00:27:20.363
farmakhn mit, mit tint, ir farshteyt, far-

00:27:20.363 --> 00:27:28.704
un mir hobn nit gevust, mir zaynen, mir, keyner hot nit gevust vos dos iz; k- ale hobn gegleybt ot azoy, dos iz ver s'iz geven ummeglekhkeyt, haynt UNK dos alts geefnt.

00:27:28.704 --> 00:27:33.477
haynt veysn mir vos dos iz geven, ober in yene tsaytn

00:27:33.477 --> 00:27:37.386
hobn mir poshet nit gevust vos es tut zikh dortn in Rusland.

00:27:37.386 --> 00:27:41.454
tsi gedenkt ir az ayer yugnt zol zayn a guter?

00:27:41.454 --> 00:27:43.999
ayer yugnt is geven a guter

00:27:43.999 --> 00:27:45.658
a freylekher yugnt?

00:27:45.921 --> 00:27:46.661
bay mir?

00:27:46.092 --> 00:27:47.117
far der milkhome.

00:27:47.117 --> 00:27:47.819
bay mir?

00:27:47.819 --> 00:27:48.632
yo.

00:27:48.632 --> 00:27:51.817
di shenste yorn iz di kindershe yorn.

00:27:51.817 --> 00:27:55.204
kh'hob shoyn aykh dertseylt s'iz geven zeyer shvere kindershe yorn.

00:27:55.204 --> 00:28:00.000
ober, over vos?

00:28:00.000 --> 00:28:03.295
s'iz geven zeyer fayn.

00:28:03.295 --> 00:28:09.727
a kind trakht vegn gornisht; er loyft aroys a borveser; er loyft aroys mit a shtikl BREAD; er loyft aroys vi ikh veys.

00:28:09.727 --> 00:28:12.227
bay mir in shtub, bay mir in shtub iz

00:28:12.227 --> 00:28:15.704
iz geven a groyser shafe, an almer a groyser.

00:28:15.704 --> 00:28:18.067
ikh gedenk, fun amolike, mit di

00:28:18.067 --> 00:28:21.613
mit di tsurelekh fun di khayes, ir veyst?

00:28:21.613 --> 00:28:24.226
un untn

00:28:24.226 --> 00:28:27.863
iz gelegn dray toyres fun dem zeydn vos m'hot tsugenumen fun sh-

00:28:27.863 --> 00:28:30.613
fun, fun, fun SYNAGOGUE.

00:28:30.613 --> 00:28:33.317
un s'iz geven zeyer a sakh tfiln.

00:28:33.317 --> 00:28:36.431
un s'iz geven zeyer a sakh talisn untn.

00:28:36.431 --> 00:28:40.408
on oybn geven zeyer a sakh bikher fun far der shul.

00:28:40.408 --> 00:28:42.862
az m'hot, az m'hot farmakht di shul

00:28:42.862 --> 00:28:45.362
hot der zeyde tsugenumen dos un

00:28:45.362 --> 00:28:50.544
ts- aheym tsu zikh, un dos iz gelegn biz vanen s'hot ongehoybn di milkhome.

00:28:50.544 --> 00:28:52.976
iz,

00:28:52.976 --> 00:28:55.794
vos hob ikh gevolt fun deroyf zogn, az s'iz

00:28:55.794 --> 00:28:59.862
az s'iz,

00:28:59.862 --> 00:29:03.317
oyf vos hobn mir zikh opgeshtelt zikh?

00:29:03.317 --> 00:29:05.712
i- ir hot dertseylt vegn ayer yugnt.

00:29:05.565 --> 00:29:08.615
ah, ye, ye, vegn mayne kindershe yorn.

00:29:08.615 --> 00:29:13.249
az, az, farshteyt zikh in almer geven zeyer a sakh tfiln

00:29:13.249 --> 00:29:16.022
mit di rimendlekh

00:29:16.022 --> 00:29:20.931
un, un, un vinter

00:29:20.931 --> 00:29:25.113
az m'hot gefarbundn oyf eyn fus a shtikl holts

00:29:25.113 --> 00:29:28.976
un s'iz nit geven mit vos farbindn, fleg ikh ah, nemen shnaydn

00:29:28.976 --> 00:29:32.317
haynt ken ikh dos UNK nit sheyn, ken aropshnaydn a shtikl

00:29:32.317 --> 00:29:33.264
fun di tfiln.

00:29:33.264 --> 00:29:34.926
ye, dem.

00:29:34.926 --> 00:29:37.476
un fleg aroystrogn, opgebn a

00:29:37.476 --> 00:29:40.545
a khaver, flegt er mir gebn a shtikl broyt mit puter.

00:29:40.545 --> 00:29:43.067
farshteyt? far deroyf.

00:29:43.067 --> 00:29:45.363
un dos iz geven, ober, s'iz geven

00:29:45.363 --> 00:29:51.227
ober s'iz geven zeyer, zeyer, s'iz geven, ikh bin geven zeyer a, a shtarker yingl, ir farshteyt?

00:29:51.227 --> 00:29:54.068
di, di gresere yinglekh hobn gevolt

